- Bindings: 18 (liveCells, x, y, count, dx, dy, cx, cy, countNeighbors, containsCell, isVerticalBlinker, result, isCell11Alive, cell11Neighbors, shouldCell11Survive, shouldCell11BeReproduced) = 18
- Invocations: 13 (countNeighbors×1, containsCell×4, some×2, length×1, push×1, isVerticalBlinker×1, &&×3) = 26
- Conditionals: 7 (if×7) = 28
- Loops: 2 (for×2) = 10
- Assignments: 4 (count =, result =, result.push) = 24

Total Mass: 13 + 18 + 26 + 28 + 10 + 24 = 119
